From now on, it is strictly forbidden: 1) Blow up the FSB building in Minecraft - what if you want to blow it up later in real life? 2) Build the FSB building in Minecraft - well, what if you want to blow it up there after that? 3) Download Minecraft - what if do you want to build an FSB building there? 4) Buy a computer - well, what if you want to download Minecraft on it? 5) Be born - well, what if at some point you want to buy a computer?